name: Spacedelivery
tagline: A space game where the player no longer tackles the dificulties of space combat, but space cargo transport.
body:
###Space Delivery
This is a game like no other.  It's for those who prefer the safe side of space travel or those who want to be known for delivering cargo between space stations. It's currently in Pre-Alpha, so don't expect much from it.  Feel free to use the source any way you'd like.


### Authors and Contributors
